<TITLE> Zillur consoles Hasina </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, May 12 (bdnews24.com)President Zillur Rahman consoled prime minister Sheikh Hasina on Tuesday over the death of her husband Dr M A Wazed Miah, an official said. Both got emotional as the president sympathised with her, the press secretary for the president said. "The president went to Jamuna at 7pm," Abdul Awal Hawlader told bdnews24.com. "He [also] talked with her privately." Rahman reminisced about his closeness with the Dr Miah, a nuclear scientist who died on Saturday after prolonged illness. b
